'''Lake Umberbool''' was a [[lake]] on [[Naboo/Legends|Naboo]], and the site of an arena for the [[Gungan/Legends|Gungan]] [[Standard year/Legends|annual]] [[Festival of Warriors]]. Shortly before the [[Battle of Naboo/Legends|Battle of Naboo]] in [[32 BBY/Legends|32 BBY]] a new arena was built at the bottom of the lake.<ref name="Adventures 10">''[[Episode I Adventures 10: Festival of Warriors]]''</ref>

==Behind the scenes==
Lake Umberbool first appeared in [[Ryder Windham]]'s [[2000]] children's book, ''[[Episode I Adventures 9: Rescue in the Core]]''.<ref name="Adventures 9">''[[Episode I Adventures 9: Rescue in the Core]]''</ref> It shared a name with [[Umberbool City]], a location mentioned in the [[2001]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] ''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]''.<ref name="GB">''[[Star Wars: Galactic Battlegrounds]]''</ref>

